Description_Lang_enUS: Defeat the mad Headless Horseman before he burns down every last settlement in Azeroth.
Defeat Ahune, the Frost Lord, before he fully manifests in Azeroth and puts an end to Summer forever.
Defeat the jealous Coren Direbrew to stop his incessant attacks upon the Brewfest festivities.
Defeat the insidious undead apothecaries of the Crown Chemical Co. before they unleash their newest, horrific plague.
